If you're looking for food that tastes as good as it looks... you've come to the right place! Carifesta is one of my go-to choices for take out! The food is made to order, and is like an explosion of flavors in your mouth. I've tried various items from their menu and have NOT been disappointed with ANYTHING i've had!  Want the best jerk chicken you'll ever eat?!?!? Then come to Carifesta!!! Their jerk chicken is my #1 favorite item on the menu. It's spicy, full of flavor.. simply to die for!! (order it with a side of mac and cheese or fried rice..oh my lord. you won't be disappointed!)  The owner and staff are so sweet! Everytime I go I'm greeted with a smile, and exceptional service! That alone makes me want to return, every single time!
